headline: Nike Relaunches ACG As Outdoor Brand While Valuation Stays In Focus
summary: Nike is relaunching its All Conditions Gear (ACG) as a dedicated outdoor brand. The company is combining Nike Trail and ACG into one outdoor performance offering. Nike is expanding product lines, opening new outdoor focused retail spaces, and creating an All Conditions Racing Department with an athlete trail team. For investors watching NIKE, NYSE:NKE, this move comes with the stock around $62.18 and a 1 year return of 16.9% decline, extending to a 53.4% decline over 5 years. Those numbers...
